This dialogue with my son made me proud of my parenting:<p>Me: &quot;Godfather I?&quot;
He: &quot;One of the greatest movies of all time.&quot;
Me: &quot;Godfather II?&quot;
He: &quot;Transcendental.  The rare sequel better than the original.&quot;
Me: &quot;Godfather III?&quot;
He: &quot;Never happened.  An elaborate hoax.&quot;
